{"tid":1292421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"眾籌買《蘋果》送比廢老","createTime":"2019-07-07T10:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T00:51:11.000Z","uid":243670,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"044a984d07ce4fadfac293db9d3bb521612cf402","tid":1292421,"uid":243670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:02:47.000Z","msg":"見到有巴打做社會實驗幫雙親like哂黃絲page<br />\n獲得空前嘅成功<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以眾籌買《蘋果》然後派比啲廢老<br />\n有免費報紙點會唔攞<br />\n仲要厚過啲免費報咁多<br />\n（唔知依家仲有冇風月版）<br />\n睇多幾個禮拜可能可以救番佢地<br />\n再喺公園再其他廢老開心share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比多啲機會佢地接觸番真正嘅世界<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》又攢到錢<br />\n又救到班無知嘅廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677a357610086c4cb2019717205d57a3e1b3d418","tid":1292421,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:03:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02eb00bdf2c01ceab9cf61baffa628e051684367","tid":1292421,"uid":241844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:05:14.000Z","msg":"幾好巴打 加油"},{"pid":"84659cdec8c0691e5b91f7d2f3ee2a6105cd0eb6","tid":1292421,"uid":30510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:24:34.000Z","msg":"幫垃圾攞黎賣嘅"},{"pid":"4f646c785e014f3c2ebe40b1536a076fbff5d4a4","tid":1292421,"uid":139704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84659cdec8c0691e5b91f7d2f3ee2a6105cd0eb6","tid":1292421,"uid":30510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:24:34.000Z","msg":"幫垃圾攞黎賣嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:51:11.000Z","msg":"一人買一份返屋企 唔好晒咗佢"}]}